title: Busted For Sweet n' Low
description:
This week, Meredith and Patton answer more speakpipes and emails. They also talk about Patton's equestrian training, Meredith meeting Justice Ketanji Brown, why you can't smuggle Sweet n' Low across the Canadian border and more!
